The paper deals with automatic photo aesthetic assessment using deep convolutional neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses visualization techniques and qualitative analysis, which are related to multimedia (cs.MM) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper deals with image retrieval and classification, which falls under information retrieval (cs.IR).
